1482:
WITH segment_consumption AS (
  SELECT 
    c.Segment,
    SUM(y.Consumption) AS total_consumption_2012,
    SUM(CASE WHEN y.Date LIKE '2013%' THEN y.Consumption ELSE 0 END) AS total_consumption_2013
  FROM customers c
  JOIN yearmonth y ON c.CustomerID = y.CustomerID
  WHERE c.Currency = 'EUR'
  GROUP BY c.Segment
),
percentage_increase AS (
  SELECT 
    Segment,
    (total_consumption_2013 - total_consumption_2012) / total_consumption_2012 * 100 AS percentage_change
  FROM segment_consumption
)
SELECT 
  Segment, 
  MAX(percentage_change) AS max_percentage_change, 
  MIN(percentage_change) AS min_percentage_change
FROM percentage_increase
WHERE Segment IN ('SME', 'LAM', 'KAM')
GROUP BY Segment;

SELECT 
  c.CustomerID,
  SUM(t1.Amount) AS TotalSpent,
  AVG(t1.Price) AS AveragePricePerItem,
  t2.Currency
FROM 
  transactions_1k t1
JOIN 
  customers c ON t1.CustomerID = c.CustomerID
JOIN 
  yearmonth ym ON c.CustomerID = ym.CustomerID
JOIN 
  (
    SELECT 
      CustomerID, 
      Currency, 
      ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY CustomerID ORDER BY SUM(Amount) DESC) AS rn
    FROM 
      transactions_1k
    GROUP BY 
      CustomerID, Currency
  ) t2 ON c.CustomerID = t2.CustomerID AND ym.Currency = t2.Currency
WHERE 
  t2.rn = 1
GROUP BY 
  c.CustomerID, t2.Currency;
